```
# Rust-specific ignores
target/
**/*.rs.bk
**/*.tmp

# Dependencies
Cargo.lock

# Logs and temp files
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*

# Editors
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# Build artifacts
**/*.o
**/*.obj
**/*.exe
**/*.dll
**/*.so
**/*.a
**/*.out

# Coverage
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# Python-related (if any Python components)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.mypy_cache/
.pytest_cache/

# Node-related (if any JS components)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
```